query:
/*+  */ select count(*)
from tag AS t1
inner join site AS s
on s.site_id = t1.site_id AND t1.name IN ('add',
'admob',
'android-animation',
'concurrency',
'mac',
'nsstring',
'powershell-2.0',
'preg-match',
'pytorch',
'responsive',
'routes',
'time-series',
'vector',
'wireless-networking') AND s.site_name IN ('stackoverflow',
'superuser')
inner join so_user AS u1
on s.site_id = u1.site_id AND u1.downvotes >= 10 AND u1.downvotes <= 100000
inner join badge AS b
on b.user_id = u1.id AND s.site_id = b.site_id AND b.name ilike '%user%'
inner join tag_question AS tq1
on t1.id = tq1.tag_id AND s.site_id = tq1.site_id
inner join answer AS a1
on s.site_id = a1.site_id AND a1.owner_user_id = u1.id
inner join account AS acc
on acc.id = u1.account_id
inner join question AS q1
on q1.id = a1.question_id AND s.site_id = q1.site_id AND q1.id = tq1.question_id AND q1.view_count >= 10 AND q1.view_count <= 1000;
